title: Conference Location
---
body:

Advances in the collective behaviour of complex systems will take place on the **Golm campus** [(Komplex II)](http://www.uni-potsdam.de/db/zeik-portal/gm/lageplan.php?komplex=2) of the University of Potsdam. <br>
The conference sessions will happen in the lecture halls of the ground floor of the Institute of Earth and Environmental Science building ([**building 27, room 0.01**, next to the Institute of Physics and Astronomy, ](http://www.uni-potsdam.de/db/zeik-portal/gm/lageplan.php?komplex=2) near the railway station). <br>
The Mensa is located in [building 4](http://www.uni-potsdam.de/db/zeik-portal/gm/lageplan.php?komplex=2).

#### Address <a name="address"></a> <a name="how-to-get-to-golm"></a>####

Institute of Earth and Environmental Science <br>
University of Potsdam <br>
Karl-Liebknecht-Str 24/25, Building 27 <br>

D-14476 Potsdam

